- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper mentions the quality of the code developed as one of the development aspects that can be improved through the use of agile practices. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a possible category as the paper discusses the management of cost and scope in software projects, which can be relevant to computational finance and science. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper mentions the improvement of team abilities as one of the development aspects that can be improved through the use of agile practices, which can be relevant to human-computer interaction.
